    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus for enhanced valve timing and lift. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp synchronization, delivering power to the rear wheels with classic 911 linearity. Critically, the IMS bearing has been addressed with an LN Engineering retrofit. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup to provide exceptional communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. It is a mechanically sorted example, showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, but remains structurally and dynamically superb.",
